# Backend conventions

- Routers under `app/routers/`, schemas under `app/schemas/`, services under `app/services/`.
- New tools: add wrapper in `deep_scan.py` or `attack.py`, register in pipeline list in `scanner.py`, optional config path in `config.py`.
- Orchestrator owns DB sessions via `SessionLocal`, emits WS events after each tool/finding, handles cancel via `asyncio.Task.cancel()`.
- Attack tools: sqlmap / dalfox / nuclei exploit — aggressive flags OK; clamp timeouts; parse stdout into structured `parsed_output`.
- Reports live in `services/report.py` (`scan_to_json`, `scan_to_html`). Prefer query `?format=` over new paths when possible.
- CVSS: map severity to a float when the tool does not provide one (info 0.0, low 3.1, medium 5.5, high 7.5, critical 9.8).
